parameters.value:
SELECT core.account_user.status FROM core.account_user
JOIN personcontact ON personcontact.person_id = core.account_user.person_id
WHERE contactvalue = 'dodgybeetroot@pkbtest.com' AND account_id =
(SELECT account_id FROM core.account_user
WHERE defaultaccount AND person_id=1819);
